quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  19,16,"JaŇčto ka Deftere Mariyama tuma nde o wo…ó…óitinoo immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyankoore"
  19,17,"O jogitii gaanin ma…ď…ďe wirngallo, Men Nuli e makko Ruuhu Amen o nanndintinanii mo e …ďanndinke fotondir…óo"
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii Yurmetee…óo On immorde e maa…óa si tawii a laatike ko a kulo [Alla]"
  19,19,"O wi'i: \"Pellet, min ko mi Nulaa…óo Joomi maa…óa fii yo mi okke suka laa…ďu…óo"
  19,20,"O wi'i: \"Ko honno laatoranta lam suka hara …ďanndinke meemaali lam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"
  19,21,"O wi'i: \"ko nii Joomi maa…óa Daaliri: \"∆äum no newii e Am e fii yo Men wa…óu mo Maande fii yim…ďe …ďen e Yurmeende immornde e Amen …óum laatike fiyaake √Ďaawaa…óo"
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure wo…ó…óitiinde"
  19,23,"Ňäata(qatwere) on fi…ói mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: \"Ee hara nun mi maayuno ko adii …óum mi laatoo huunde yejjitaande"
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wata a suno gom…óii Joomi maa…óa wa…óii ley maa…óa caangol"
  19,25,Ye∆īu(dimmbu) faade e maa…óa jullere tamarohi kin nde li…ďa e maa…óa …ďenndu…óe te…ďetee…óe
  19,26,"√Ďaamu yaraa …ďu…ď…ďinaa gite, si a yi'ii go…ó…óo immorde e …ďanndinke wi'u: \"Min dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotoo…óo korka mi wowlidata e ne…ó…óanke hannde)"
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yim…ďe makko, himo tammbii mo …ďe wi'i: \"Ko an yo Mariyama gom…óii a addii huunde hawnii nde"
  19,28,Ko an yo banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki ne…ó…óo bon…óo neene maa…óa kadi laataaki jeenoowo=jinoowo
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, …ďe wi'i:\"Ko honno men yewtirta e on sanfaajo won…óo e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu"
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: \"Min dey ko mi jeyaa…óo Alla O Okkii lam Deftere nden O Wa…óii lam Annabaajo"
  19,31,"O Wa…ói lam Barkinaa…óo nokku kala ka mi woni, O Wasiyii lam Julde nden e Jakka on fodde mi…óo wuuri"
  19,32,"Ko mi …óiggan…óo yumma am, O wa…óaali lam ndunndarankeejo malkisaa…óo"
  19,33,Kisiyee on wonii e am √Īalnde mi jibinaa e √Īal- nde mi maayata e √Ďalnde mi immintintee ko mi wuuru…óo
  19,34,On ko Iisaa ge…óal Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol hi…ďe sikkitoo fii mu'un
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde O jogitotoo …ďi…ó…óo Senayee wonanii Mo, si O √Ďaawii fiyaake O Daalanay mo tun: \"Wonu\" o wona"
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, Rewee Mo. Ko …óum woni Laawol Focciingol"
  19,37,"Feddeeji …óin luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii …ďen yeddu…ďe seedagol √Ďalaande Mawnde"
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa ma…ď…ďe √Ďalnde …ďe aroyta e Amen, kono too√Īoo…ďe …ďen hannde hi…ďe e nder majjere …ďanngunde"
  19,39,"Hul…ďinir …ďe √Ďalnde Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on √Īaawaa hara kam…ďe hi…ďe e nder welsindaare hara …ďe gom…óinaa"
  19,40,"Menen Men ronay leydi ndin e …ďen wonu…ďe e dow mayri, ko ka Amen …ďe ruttetee"